    <h1 class="about-title">About Alba Tull</h1>
    <div class="about-content">
      <p>Alba Tull is a contemporary photographer whose work spans continents and cultures. With a focus on light, color, and human connection, her images capture moments that resonate across borders.</p>

      <p>Based between New York and Europe, Alba has spent over two decades exploring diverse landscapes — from the canals of Amsterdam to the lavender fields of Provence, the temples of Japan to the coastal villages of Portugal.</p>

      <p>Her work has appeared in numerous publications and exhibitions worldwide. Alba believes photography is a language that transcends words, a way to share stories, emotions, and the extraordinary beauty found in everyday moments.</p>

      <p>Each photograph in this collection represents a journey, a discovery, or a fleeting moment of clarity. Through her lens, the familiar becomes remarkable, and the overlooked becomes unforgettable.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
